item.title: IEEE International Conference on Robotics and Automation 2016
item.description:
The KTH hosted the IEEE International Conference on Robotics and Automation 2016 in Stockholm this year. We organized and ran a fabulous conference under gernal chair Danica Kragic.

Pictures from the conference are avaialbe for download at the conference website.
